{"tid":1503883,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 警察朋友請入 ] 我朋友做麥當勞","createTime":"2019-08-25T06:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:27:25.000Z","uid":48259,"like":94,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6d233cc132997977cdc83730c08ab5d827dbb806","tid":1503883,"uid":48259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:11:46.000Z","msg":"建議你地真係唔好為左六折優惠而自稱警察<br />\n我有朋友做麥當勞一個月前已經同我講<br />\n佢地一知係警察就會<strong>一撚定會加料</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地咁都做得出，我一定會罷食！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">支持警察，唔食垃圾！！！！</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c074732cc52b16dd53bba1d65ee7622d736004e","tid":1503883,"uid":48259,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"跌左落地下嘅豬柳強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e218a5e3480ec96351d49edbe5983fbaa05c8de","tid":1503883,"uid":48259,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:14:51.000Z","msg":"白汁魚柳包 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12bb11c16c1f46b4d04599b536befce82e69b70b","tid":1503883,"uid":110509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,待定, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有機9月6(五)搞埋</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: orang